      "groupKey": "listening-part-2",
      "passage": {
        "title": "The Green Valley adventure race",
        "text": "Last spring, teams from four schools joined the Green Valley adventure race. They canoed across the river, then cycled along muddy tracks. One team got lost because their map blew away, but a volunteer helped them. The winning team finished in two hours and donated their prize money to plant trees."
      },
      "note": "Text-simulated listening — no audio."
    },
